  Clip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1450cabce03176d4f8d19e7c117076fa, type: 3}
  Subtitles: "So anyway, my best friend and I, we wanted to like do this one military
    reenactment thing in the forest? So I\u2019m there, and so is BFF, and this cute
    little half-Thai dude who looks amazing in a partisan outfit, like, I wish we
    could get him for our reenactment group because his little ass would look so
    good in the tropical uniform\u2026 But of course, Thai-dude brought a third buddy,
    and like - none of us knew this third guy. Would it be rude to look for red flags
    if you\u2019re just looking to get laid?"
